1
00:00:12,320 --> 00:00:13,080
In the ancient

2
00:00:13,080 --> 00:00:15,160
Mesopotamian plains,

3
00:00:15,640 --> 00:00:17,039
there lived the beautiful

4
00:00:17,039 --> 00:00:18,519
goddess Inanna.

5
00:00:19,160 --> 00:00:20,640
Legend says

6
00:00:20,760 --> 00:00:23,679
she was the goddess of love and justice.

7
00:00:24,679 --> 00:00:25,960
Then, one day,

8
00:00:26,399 --> 00:00:28,160
Inanna, high in the heavens,

9
00:00:28,359 --> 00:00:30,199
suddenly heard

10
00:00:30,199 --> 00:00:32,759
a wail from the underworld.

11
00:00:33,320 --> 00:00:34,759
It was the voice

12
00:00:34,960 --> 00:00:36,159
of her younger sister,

13
00:00:36,159 --> 00:00:38,119
Ereshkigal, Queen of the Underworld.

14
00:00:38,880 --> 00:00:39,719
So,

15
00:00:39,960 --> 00:00:41,240
Inanna passed through

16
00:00:41,240 --> 00:00:43,280
the narrow Seven Gates of the Underworld

17
00:00:43,520 --> 00:00:45,880
to visit her suffering sister.

18
00:00:46,320 --> 00:00:47,759
But unexpectedly,

19
00:00:48,240 --> 00:00:50,640
Ereshkigal screamed frantically,

20
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:52,320
"I will grind her

21
00:00:52,320 --> 00:00:53,759
into dead ashes!"

22
00:00:54,399 --> 00:00:55,679
She repaid Inanna's kindness

23
00:00:55,840 --> 00:00:58,119
with pure rage.

24
00:00:59,799 --> 00:01:00,920
After that,

25
00:01:01,280 --> 00:01:02,920
Inanna remained

26
00:01:02,920 --> 00:01:04,640
forever in the painful

27
00:01:04,640 --> 00:01:05,640
underworld.

28
00:01:06,560 --> 00:01:07,879
While the furious

29
00:01:07,879 --> 00:01:08,959
Ereshkigal

30
00:01:09,439 --> 00:01:11,400
wore her sister's crown,

31
00:01:12,079 --> 00:01:13,200
relishing the glory

32
00:01:13,560 --> 00:01:15,799
that once belonged to her sister,

33
00:01:15,920 --> 00:01:17,079
along with the power.

34
00:01:24,040 --> 00:01:25,519
Your hand is injured.

35
00:01:26,480 --> 00:01:27,280
Does it hurt?

36
00:01:28,879 --> 00:01:29,519
How could you

37
00:01:29,519 --> 00:01:31,040
