43
00:01:43,519 --> 00:01:44,239
Don't worry,

44
00:01:44,239 --> 00:01:46,280
this treatment is very safe

45
00:01:46,280 --> 00:01:47,439
with minimal side effects.

46
00:01:47,480 --> 00:01:49,040
For Rao Yuci's current condition,

47
00:01:49,040 --> 00:01:50,200
