125
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:00,120
Mom!

126
00:05:00,519 --> 00:05:01,319
Mom!

127
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:02,240
Let me go!

128
00:05:02,240 --> 00:05:04,279
